name: 早坂愛 - Ai Hayasaka - Kaguya-Sama:Love is War.
description:
2nd Version is out!

See changes notes!

Posting my Second Lora Release, 早坂愛 - Ai Hayasaka From Kaguya-Sama, I know there other on Civitai or HF, but i wanted one With Better Quality & More flexible, So i created one that's i like.

Put everything in Filter for seeing all images!

He can do pratically Anime like Ai Hayakasa With the Good Model or Flexible Art Like with Abyss or Meina Model.

Trained on 346+ Images with Good quality. (SFW + And some NFSW)

Weight: Recommended: 0.6-1 - Best Result: 0.8-1 Works perfectly at 1.

Model used: AbyssOrangeMix2_hard, MechanixMix, Anime ScreenShot-Like, YesMix, Corneo's 7th Heaven mix, MeinaMix.

But probably works with any Anime Model.

Also i tested it on Realistic model, he work too.

He can do the base Default skin Pretty well, and can be Flexible to other outfit too, better to reduce the weight to 0.8 sometime but at 1 it's work fine. (See examples images)

AnimeFullFinalPrunedFP16 used for Training, so it's work with pratically all the Anime Model.

Will add more Image with time.

Trigger words is in the prompt image examples.

Just the basic for really Activating Ai Hayasaka Lora is AiHayasakaV4, but you need to describe a little bit for Best Result, like in the Image examples.

Negative Embedding used: EasyNegative, BadPrompt2.

Share you're image in Comments :).

  4. Better Faces, Clothes, Hands & Flexibility, Better precision.

  5. Reducted the Number of prompts needed to Trigger Ai Hayasaka.
